description: Acoustic covers of some of the greatest songs of the 80s and 90s. The 1980s and 1990s were very different musically, but both were great decades that produced unforgettable songs. If you're a fan of 80s and 90s music, as well as acoustic covers, you'll love this 80s and 90s Acoustic Covers playlist.
